-## Sample Library V9 Live Metadata Mix
-
-- Created rollback archive:
-  `Docs/Design/SampleLibraryArchive/2026-05-04-before-v9-live-metadata-mix/`.
-- Added a per-item sample metadata policy so real launch links can opt into a
-  one-time live metadata refresh while fake utility/admin samples preserve
-  their generated thumbnails.
-- Added a real YouTube sample near the top:
-  `Inside the Mind of a Master Procrastinator | Tim Urban | TED`, using
-  YouTube metadata and thumbnail.
-- Converted top real links for PubMed, Anthropic, NCI/Cancer, and NASA to use
-  actual metadata/image URLs instead of SAVI-generated editorial art.
-- Bumped the native sample seed version to `12`; main `SAVI` refreshed to
-  72 sample saves and was cloned into `SAVI Test` for simulator parity.
-- Built and installed both simulator channels, then captured QA screenshot:
-  `/Users/guest1/Desktop/SAVI_QA/savi_v9_live_metadata_home_2026-05-04.png`.
